title: Good Luck Trying to Tell the Difference Between This La La Land Dance Tribute and the Original
text:
Carson Dean's La La Land Dance Tribute Video Good Luck Trying to Tell the Difference Between This La La Land Dance Tribute and the Original February 4, 2017 by Monica Sisavat 0 Shares 
With its stunning choreography and incredible singing, it's pretty clear why La La Land has been sweeping award season . Choreographers Carson Dean and Kausha Campbell paid tribute to the talented cast and crew earlier this week by recreating the "Lovely Night Dance" from the film, and yes, it's as amazing as it sounds. Not only do they completely nail the routine, but Carson and Kausha watched the film over a dozen times to make sure the dance was exactly like the one in the movie. Watch it above now. Related:
